<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>LALS&#160;256.  European-Indigenous Interaction in Latin America.  3 hours.</strong></p>
<p class="courseblockdesc">
Responses of indigenous societies in Latin America to colonization by people from the Old World. The historical and social circumstances of contact and culture change will be covered.  Course Information:  Same as <a href="/search/?P=ANTH%20256" title="ANTH&#160;256" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ANTH 256');">ANTH&#160;256</a>.<i>  World Cultures course</i>.<br />
