<p class="courseblockdesc">
Survey of the contemporary indigenous cultures of Meso-America, studied against their pre-conquest history and in their development since the Spanish Conquest. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=ANTH%20277" title="ANTH&#160;277" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ANTH 277');">ANTH&#160;277</a>. Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=ENGL%20161" title="ENGL&#160;161" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'ENGL 161');">ENGL&#160;161</a>.<i>  Individual and Society course, and  World Cultures course</i>.<br />
