<p class="courseblockdesc">
Latin American women in historical perspective from pre-Columbian and Iberian societies to the present. Course Information: Same as <a href="/search/?P=GWS%20275" title="GWS&#160;275" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'GWS 275');">GWS&#160;275</a> and <a href="/search/?P=POLS%20275" title="POLS&#160;275" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'POLS 275');">POLS&#160;275</a>. Class Schedule Information: To be properly registered, students must enroll in one Lecture and one Discussion/Recitation.<i>  Past course, and  World Cultures course</i>.<br />
